ust settings\"}],\" — Optionally tweak CRF, resolution, and audio settings for precise control.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Compress\"}],\" — Click Compress and wait. The progress bar shows real-time status. Video encoding is CPU-intensive and may take a few minutes.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Download\"}],\" — When complete, see the before/after file size and click Download.\"]}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Video Compressor\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"CRF beats bitrate for predictable quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],\"$L2d\"]}],\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\"]}]]}],\"$L31\",\"$L32\"],\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\"]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0u6_wxl0ai9fm.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"$L37\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$29\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@38\"}]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"CRF beats bitrate for predictable quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Constant Rate Factor (CRF 18–28 for H.264) targets visual quality directly. A bitrate target is a budget that the encoder fills regardless of complexity. CRF gives consistent quality; bitrate gives consistent file size.\"}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Drop resolution before dropping quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Drop resolution before dropping quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"A 1080p video at CRF 23 looks better and is smaller than a 4K video at CRF 30. If the destination doesn't need 4K (most don't), downscale first.\"}]]}]]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Preview the projected file size before committing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Preview the projected file size before committing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The tool estimates output size from your settings. If the estimate is still too big, lower the bitrate or raise the CRF before running the compression — not after.\"}]]}]]}]\n30:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use H.265 for archives, H.264 for sharing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use H.265 for archives, H.264 for sharing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"HEVC compresses ~30–50% better but isn't universally playable. For long-term storage where you control playback, HEVC wins. For sharing, stick to H.264.\"}]]}]]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Compressing an already-compressed video twice\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Compressing an already-compressed video twice\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Every compression pass loses quality. If a video has been compressed once already, re-compressing it for a small additional saving is rarely worth the quality hit.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Targeting an exact file size for an unknown duration\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$31:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Targeting an exact file size for an unknown duration\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Bitrate × duration = file size. Telling the encoder \\\"make it 25 MB\\\" without knowing duration produces unpredictable quality. Decide quality first, accept the size that follows.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Compressing screen recordings to high CRF\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$31:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Compressing screen recordings to high CRF\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Screen recordings have lots of sharp edges (text, UI) that compress poorly at high CRF. Use lower CRF (18–22) for screen content, higher (23–28) for natural video.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Key Takeaways\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"cla