ons, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\\\",\\\"worksFor\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Free Tool Shed\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"Built and maintained by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\",\"rel\":\"author\",\"children\":\"James Nicolaus\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]\n1e:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Summary\",\"className\":\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Shrink video file size with adjustable quality (CRF), resolution, and bitrate controls — running entirely in your browser via ffmpeg.wasm. Preview the projected before/after size before exporting. Supports MP4, MOV, MKV, WebM, and AVI. No sign-up, no upload — a free alternative to VEED Pro, Clipchamp, and HandBrake.\"}]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Quality Presets\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Choose Small File, Balanced, or High Quality — or set a custom CRF value for precise control over the quality/size trade-off.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Resolution Control\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Optionally downscale to 1080p, 720p, 480p, or 360p while maintaining aspect ratio. Great for cutting file size further.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"H.264 + AAC Output\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Output is MP4 with H.264 video and AAC audio — the most universally compatible format for web, mobile, and social media.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"100% Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All processing happens in your browser using WebAssembly. Your video never leaves your device — no uploads, no servers.\"}]]}]]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2c\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"not-prose mb-10\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Video Compressor — Reduce Video Size Online\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The Free Video Compressor lets you reduce video file size directly in your browser using H.264 (libx264) encoding via WebAssembly. Choose a quality preset or fine-tune with custom CRF and resolution settings. Your video never leaves your device — no uploads, no sign-up, no file size limits.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Quality presets\"}],\" — Small File, Balanced, High Quality, or Custom. Each preset configures CRF and resolution for the best results.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"CRF control\"}],\" — Fine-tune the quality/size trade-off with a slider from 0 (lossless) to 51 (maximum compression).\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Resolution downscaling\"}],\" — Reduce from 4K to 1080p, 720p, 480p, or 360p while maintaining aspect ratio.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Audio passthrough\"}],\" — Copy the audio stream without re-encoding for faster processing, or re-encode to AAC 128k.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"MP4 output\"}],\" — H.264 + AAC with faststart flag for instant web playback. Compatible with every device and platform.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"100% client-side\"}],\" — Uses ffmpeg.wasm (WebAssembly). Your video never leaves your device.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How to Compress a Video\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"1. Add a video\"}],\" — Drag and drop a video file or click to browse. Supports MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, MKV.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"2. Choose a preset\"}],\" — Select Small File for maximum compression, Balanced for a good trade-off, or High Quality for minimal loss.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Adjust settings\"}],\" — Optionally tweak CRF, resolution, and audio settings for precise control.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Compress\"}],\" — Click Compress and wait. The progress bar shows real-time status. Video encoding is CPU-intensive and may take a few minutes.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Download\"}],\" — When complete, see the before/after file size and click Download.\"]}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Video Compressor\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"CRF beats bitrate for predictable quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],\"$L2d\"]}],\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\"]}]]}],\"$L31\",\"$L32\"],\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\"]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0u6_wxl0ai9fm.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"$L37\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$29\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@38\"}]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"CRF beats bitrate for predictable quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Constant Rate Factor (CRF 18–28 for H.264) targets visual quality directly. A bitrate target is a budget that the encoder fills regardless of complexity. CRF gives consistent quality; bitrate gives consistent file size.\"}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Drop resolution before dropping quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Drop resolution before dropping quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"A 1080p video at CRF 23 looks better and is smaller than a 4K video at CRF 30. If the destination doesn't need 4K (most don't), downscale first.\"}]]}]]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Preview the projected file size before committing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Preview the projected file size before committing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The tool estimates output size from your settings. If the estimate is still too big, lower the bitrate or raise the CRF before running the compression — not after.\"}]]}]]}]\n30:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use H.265 for archives, H.264 for sharing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use H.265 for archives, H.264 for sharing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"HEVC compresses ~30–50% better but isn't universally playable. For long-term storage where you control playback, HEVC wins. For sharing, stick to H.264.\"}]]}]]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Compressing an already-compressed video twice\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Compressing an already-compressed video twice\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Every compression pass loses quality. If a video has been compressed once already, re-compressing it for a small additional saving is rarely worth the quality hit.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Targeting an exact file size f