Chromebooks or work machines. Use HandBrake for long videos, batch processing, or when you need maximum encoding speed.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"What CRF should I use?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"CRF 18-20 is visually lossless for most content. CRF 23-26 is a good balance of quality and size. CRF 28-32 produces noticeably softer video but much smaller files — fine for low-motion content like presentations or screen recordings.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Can I compress a 4K video to 1080p?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"Yes. Set the Max Resolution to 1080p and the video will be downscaled while maintaining aspect ratio. Combined with CRF compression, this can reduce a 4K video to 10-20% of its original size.\"}]]}]]}]\n27:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n39:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n2a:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Free Video Compressor Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Reduce video file size with quality presets or custom CRF. H.264 encoding in your browser — no uploads. A free alternative to HandBrake. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"google-adsense-account\",\"content\":\"ca-pub-7700405385978151\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit/video